jekyll+github+markdown

Installation

Requirements
		Ruby
		RubyGems
		Linux, Unix, or Mac OS X
		NodeJS, or another JavaScript runtime (for CoffeeScript support).


Install with RubyGems

	$ gem install jekyll

		ERROR:  Could not find a valid gem 'jekyll' (>= 0), here is why:
          Unable to download data from https://rubygems.org/ - Errno::ECONNREFUSED: Connection refused - connect(2) (https://api.rubygems.org/latest_specs.4.8.gz)

    	进入rubygems官网  http://rubygems.org/pages/download

    	$ gem update --system 

    	-bash: $: command not found

    	安装Ruby
    		https://ruby-china.org/wiki/install_ruby_guide


     $ gem install jekyll
	 $ jekyll new myblog
	 $ cd myblog
     $ jekyll serve
     	yutao-iMac:myblog sina$ jekyll serve
